╔IN MEMORY OF A DARLING SON, BROTHER AND UNCLE
GOOD FRIEND AND COLLEAGUE
MARIO (JAMES SEABROOK) RICHMOND POSTMAN
29.5.7 ~ 22.04.07
ALWAYS HAPPY, HARD WORKING AND GENEROUS
HE WILL NEVER BE FORGOTTEN"ķ
µIn memory of
TONY & SHEILA MOORE
06.09.33 - 18.02.94
21.04.34 - 18.08.99
from Julie. Woody. Fenton & Bailey-Rose: your daughter and her family
that you never got to meet, May they come to know you as we all sit here together."¶
